                    APPLICATION FOR VA EDUCATION BENEFITS
                    -------------------------------------

<%= disclosures(@applicant) %>


                            APPLICANT INFORMATION
                            ---------------------

SSN: <%= @applicant.veteranSocialSecurityNumber %>         Sex: <%= @applicant.gender %>             Date of Birth: <%= @applicant.veteranDateOfBirth %>

